    <summary>Enabling Certificates and CPD Hours</summary>
    <ul>
      <li>Turn on certificate generation for your courses.</li>
      <li>Set minimum completion requirements for students to earn certificates.</li>
      <li>Specify CPD hours which reflect course duration and learning activities.</li>
      <li>Courses can be aligned with industry and professional body accreditations.</li>
    </ul>
  </details>
  <h1>Earnings & Payment Details</h1>
  <details>
    <summary>Commission Structure & Payment</summary>
    <ul>
      <li>Trainers earn 20% commission of course sales revenue.</li>
      <li>Payments are processed monthly by the 15th, provided minimum threshold is met.</li>
      <li>Payment methods include M-PESA, PayPal, bank transfers, and more.</li>
      <li>Track your earnings and payments with real-time dashboard analytics.</li>
    </ul>
